Returns the precision of the field_

_Precision is the specified column size. For numeric data, this is the maximum precision. For character_data, this is the length in characters. For datetime datatypes, this is the length in characters of the_String representation (assuming the maximum allowed defaultPrecision of the fractional seconds component).
